# /oss-flow — Open Source Hub Workflow

**Trigger:** Run ONLY when the user message is exactly `/oss-flow` or starts with `/oss-flow`. Otherwise ignore this rule.

Follow `~/.cursor/commands/oss-flow.md` in full.

**Isolation (MOST IMPORTANT):** Upstream tests/repro ONLY in isolated envs (`~/dev/`, `~/oss/`, venv, VM, Docker). NEVER install global tools or modify this machine's work/system setup. If not isolated → STOP. See `OpenSource/ISOLATION.md`.

**Identity (STRICT):** `gh api user -q .login` must be `AsifAd` — else STOP, `gh auth switch`. Re-check before commit/push/PR.

**Testing mandatory before push** — full E2E + all upstream scenarios in isolated env only.
